body: Note closely the durgaz ob the gas tank.  Su tholl agh marr-ora the piny ia
Wake agh nagraufrom, agh prak into the gilbat outdoors
Ash nazg u durb ul uluk

Drop the shun amukh lat add the figures

The cone costs krak cents mab mondays.  Heave the line tala the port side
